{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC12_KYL_510.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2a,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Mix Master, so what's this problem that you wanted to talk to me about...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, well, it's not really a problem...<CR>I just wanted you to hear me out."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa8,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I don't know where to start...<CR>So I guess I'll start with this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa9,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Thinking back, my entire life so far has been a difficult struggle against this guy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Alcohol? Don't you think you're exaggerating...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa9,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I'm not exaggerating. Because of this guy, I've gone through some really tough times."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa9,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "It's weird for the owner of a tavern to not be able to drink a single drop..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa9,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I've already put in more than my fair share of effort into being able to drink."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xaa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I've repeatedly put myself through hellish training that I don't even want to recall..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Repeatedly...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Yes, and...I still can't drink the slightest bit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Well, not being able to drink is a natural talent. At least, I've decided to think of it in that way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "But...well I don't see why there can't be one tavern owner who can't drink."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x113,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, you're so nice, but the world just doesn't work that way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "A tavern owner who can't drink...<CR>The life of a man being branded as<CR>such is cruel and bleak."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "However, it got me thinking...<CR>If everyone is drinking alcohol,<CR>then I just need to eat more food!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I see!<CR>...Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "And when the drunks start getting boisterous, then that'll be my cue."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I don't mean to brag, but I'm pretty good at being boisterous, even when I'm not drunk."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I bet no one can beat me when it comes to this!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x182,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "So with that being said, I've successfully conquered my weakness of not being able to drink."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I-I don't know if that's conquering... Actually, what did you want to talk to me about?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I'm getting to the very core of the issue. It's about Juris."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "He's been getting too conceited lately, just because he can drink."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I-I see... Conceited..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "But Juris seems a bit more playful when he's with you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa8,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "He's a showoff, but in reality,<CR>he's still pretty childish."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xab,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "And I, the nice guy that I am, accept him like that. However...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "He's gone too far this time...<CR>I need to teach him a lesson."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "This is the main thing. While I was eating with him few days ago..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "He stealthily mixed alcohol into my drink!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Can you believe that!? That's why..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa6,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "I've decided that I need to exact decisive revenge against that mischievous kid!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "M-Mix Master, you've got a mischievous expression on your face right now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "That's because it's an eye for an eye, and a drink for a drink! So..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "I'm gonna sneak an adult taste that Juris hates into his food!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Since you're both adults...I'm not sure if that's really the right approach..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, that's all I wanted to tell you. Man, I can't wait to see his expression!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "I-I don't really think you had to tell me about this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Well, just look forward to it. I'll let you know how it goes next time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "(Guys are so... Oh, I was about to think something that I should never say...)"
        }
    ]
}